snippet.title: Lucky Penguin NES Trailer - Mega Cat Studios Video Game
snippet.description:
Get ready for some arctic action on your NES! Lucky Penguin is an all new top down puzzle game released by Mega Cat Studios. Guide your little penguin through a variety of ice cold challenges. Be amazed by the stunning visuals, brought to you by Flick-O-Vision. 
Programming by Lukasz Kur
Art and Design by Marcelo Barbosa


Grab your copy today!
https://megacatstudios.com/collections/nes-games/products/lucky-penguin-1

Come join in on the discussion at our official Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/megacat

Make sure to follow us on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter for updates on future releases! Follow us @megacatstudios

Lucky Penguin is not licensed, sponsored, published, or endorsed by Nintendo Co. Ltd, or their affiliates.

Mega Cat Studios is an independent games development studio. This title is an unofficial and unlicensed release for the Nintendo console, and is not affiliated with Nintendo Co., Ltd, or their affiliates. 

Nintendo® and Famicom® are trademarks of Nintendo Co., Ltd.
For more on Mega Cat Studios and our games, please visit: https://megacatstudios.com/

Come play & talk on discord! www.discord.gg/megacat
